In the 1980's the Shiskine community has managed to retain many of the caring and supporting values which appear to be passing in other parts of the country. For example, the involvement in community life, and the interest of the whole community in the work of the school, has continued. One reason for this may be the existence of the extended family in the area. { {Thanks are due to the pupils and staff {of Shiskine Primary School and to all {those who generously helped in the {task of compiling this disc. }
